static.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251700/extras/c583d2adf8d4e19f51d83f85d53af003.webm?t=1728998863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251700/extras/c583d2adf8d4e19f51d83f85d53af003.mp4?t=1728998863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>释放独特的超能力 – 每个英雄，每场战斗！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251700/extras/e8a55ecf2d820db07471f48f747201cb.poster.avif?t=1728998863\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251700/extras/e8a55ecf2d820db07471f48f747201cb.webm?t=1728998863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3251700/extras/e8a55ecf2d820db07471f48f747201cb.mp4?t=1728998863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有趣的 <strong><u>多人</u></strong> 拳击游戏，《战斗帮》中你和你的朋友们在疯狂的竞技场中展开激烈对抗。选择独特角色，施展狂野动作，并利用环境取胜。从把对手扔下屋顶到避开奇怪的陷阱，每场比赛都是一场疯狂的冒险。你准备好带领团队了吗？</p>",
